msgid "Create preliminary .cvsignore in the current directory"
msgstr "वर्तमाननिर्देशिकायां प्रारम्भिकं .cvsignore रचयन्तु"

#. Tag: title
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>create_cvsignore</command> is used to create a preliminary "
"<filename>.cvsignore</filename> in the current directory. It does this based "
"on certain contents it finds in <filename>Makefile.am</filename>"
msgstr ""
"<command>create_cvsignore</command> इत्यस्य उपयोगः वर्तमाननिर्देशिकायां प्रारम्भिकं "
"<filename>.cvsignore</filename> निर्मातुं भवति । <filename>Makefile.am</"
"filename> इत्यत्र प्राप्यमाणानां कतिपयानां सामग्रीनां आधारेण एतत् करोति"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No lines will be removed from any existing <filename>.cvsignore</filename>. "
"If there is not already a <filename>.cvsignore</filename> file, it will be "
"added to the cvs repository."
msgstr ""
"विद्यमानस्य कस्यापि <filename>.cvsignore</filename> तः कोऽपि पङ्क्तिः न निष्कासिता "
"भविष्यति । यदि पूर्वमेव <filename>.cvsignore</filename> सञ्चिका नास्ति तर्हि cvs "
"भण्डारे योजितं भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that you must have a <filename>Makefile.am</filename> in the current "
"directory for this tool to work."
msgstr ""
"ध्यानं कुर्वन्तु यत् एतत् साधनं कार्यं कर्तुं भवतः वर्तमाननिर्देशिकायां <filename>Makefile.am</"
"filename> भवितुमर्हति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr "एषा उपयोगिता &kde; सॉफ्टवेयर विकास किट।"
